    <title>&quot;drafts4&quot; tag persists even when no drafts has it</title>
    <link>https://forums.getdrafts.com/t/drafts4-tag-persists-even-when-no-drafts-has-it/12028</link>
    <description>I renamed the &quot;drafts4&quot; tag to &quot;z - drafts4&quot; so that it would sort to the bottom of the list.

I have confirmed that there are no longer any drafts tagged with &quot;drafts4&quot;.

*(Note: using Drafts on iPad Pro (12.9-inch) (3rd generation) running iPadOS 15.3.)*

**Expected:** &quot;drafts4&quot; would no longer appear in tag filter list.

**Observed:** &quot;drafts4&quot; still appears in tag filter list, as does &quot;z - drafts4&quot; (see screenshot).

