      <item>
        <title>&quot;drafts4&quot; tag persists even when no drafts has it</title>
        <dc:creator><![CDATA[Matt_Fischer]]></dc:creator>
        <description><![CDATA[
            <p>I renamed the “drafts4” tag to “z - drafts4” so that it would sort to the bottom of the list.</p>
<p>I have confirmed that there are no longer any drafts tagged with “drafts4”.</p>
<p><em>(Note: using Drafts on iPad Pro (12.9-inch) (3rd generation) running iPadOS 15.3.)</em></p>
<p><strong>Expected:</strong> “drafts4” would no longer appear in tag filter list.</p>
<p><strong>Observed:</strong> “drafts4” still appears in tag filter list, as does “z - drafts4” (see screenshot).</p>
